overview.en: The decentralized Token of open governance of DAO architecture integrates powerful defi smart contract to achieve balance in circulation, pledge and output, and has strong scalability and value carrying capacity.
overview.zh: DAO 架构开放治理的去中心化令牌，集成了强大的 defi 智能合约，并引用“铸币曲线”实现了在 流通、质押、产出等环节的供需平衡，在 NFT 及 Metaverse 等领域具有很强的扩展性和价值承载 能力。
